
UPDATE announcement_post SET translations = '{"de":{"title":"Finden Sie Ihre perfekte Playlist-Übereinstimmung mit Playlists to Pitch!","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Finden Sie Ihr perfektes Playlist-Match mit Playlists to Pitch!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Suchen Sie nach den perfekten Playlists, um Ihren Track zu pitchen? Unser neues "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"Feature nimmt das Rätselraten aus der Playlist-Ansprache heraus, indem es Playlists empfiehlt, die speziell auf Ihren Track zugeschnitten sind."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Jede Empfehlung kommt mit einer Fit Analysis, die genau erklärt, warum wir denken, dass die Playlist ein starkes Match ist - so können Sie mit Vertrauen pitchen und verpassen nie eine Gelegenheit, Ihren Track wachsen zu lassen."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Sie sehen auch wichtige Metriken auf einen Blick: Added Reach, Added Streams und direkte Links, um Playlist-Kuratoren zu erreichen."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Gehen Sie zu einer beliebigen Track Page, klicken Sie auf den Playlist-Tab und beginnen Sie noch heute, Ihre nächste Playlist-Platzierung zu entdecken!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"es":{"title":"¡Encuentra tu Lista de Reproducción Perfecta con Playlists to Pitch!","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"¡Encuentra Tu Playlist Perfecta con Playlists to Pitch!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"¿Buscas las playlists perfectas para promocionar tu canción? Nuestra nueva función "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"elimina las conjeturas del alcance a playlists al recomendar playlists diseñadas específicamente para tu canción."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Cada recomendación viene con un Análisis de Compatibilidad que explica exactamente por qué creemos que la playlist es una excelente opción - para que puedas promocionar con confianza y nunca pierdas una oportunidad de hacer crecer tu canción."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"También verás métricas clave de un vistazo: Alcance Agregado, Streams Agregados y enlaces directos para contactar a los curadores de playlists."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"¡Dirígete a cualquier Página de Canción, haz clic en la pestaña Playlist y comienza a descubrir tu próxima colocación en playlist hoy!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"fr":{"title":"Trouvez Votre Playlist Parfaite avec Playlists to Pitch !","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Trouvez Votre Playlist Parfaite avec Playlists to Pitch !"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Vous cherchez les playlists parfaites pour proposer votre titre ? Notre nouvelle fonctionnalité "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"élimine les approximations dans la prospection de playlists en recommandant des playlists spécifiquement adaptées à votre titre."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Chaque recommandation est accompagnée d''une Analyse de Compatibilité expliquant exactement pourquoi nous pensons que la playlist est un excellent match - pour que vous puissiez proposer en toute confiance et ne jamais manquer une opportunité de faire grandir votre titre."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Vous verrez aussi les métriques clés d''un coup d''œil : Portée Ajoutée, Streams Ajoutés, et des liens directs pour contacter les curateurs de playlists."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Rendez-vous sur n''importe quelle Page de Titre, cliquez sur l''onglet Playlist, et commencez dès aujourd''hui à découvrir votre prochain placement en playlist !"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"ja":{"title":"Playlists to Pitchで完璧なプレイリストマッチを見つけよう！","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Playlists to Pitchで完璧なプレイリストマッチを見つけよう！"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"あなたの楽曲にピッチする完璧なプレイリストをお探しですか？新しい "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"機能は、あなたの楽曲に特化してカスタマイズされたプレイリストを推薦することで、プレイリストへのアプローチの推測作業を不要にします。"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"各推薦には、なぜそのプレイリストが強力なマッチだと考えるのかを正確に説明するFit Analysisが付属しているため、自信を持ってピッチでき、楽曲を成長させる機会を逃すことはありません。"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"また、一目で重要な指標を確認できます：Added Reach、Added Streams、そしてプレイリストキュレーターに連絡するための直接リンクです。"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"任意のTrack Pageにアクセスし、Playlistタブをクリックして、今日から次のプレイリスト掲載を発見し始めましょう！"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"ko":{"title":"Playlists to Pitch로 완벽한 플레이리스트 매치를 찾으세요!","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Playlists to Pitch로 완벽한 플레이리스트 매치를 찾아보세요!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"당신의 트랙을 피칭할 완벽한 플레이리스트를 찾고 계신가요? 저희의 새로운 "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"기능은 당신의 트랙에 특별히 맞춤화된 플레이리스트를 추천하여 플레이리스트 아웃리치의 추측을 없애줍니다."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"각 추천에는 해당 플레이리스트가 왜 강력한 매치인지 정확히 설명하는 Fit Analysis가 포함되어 있어 - 자신감을 갖고 피칭하고 트랙을 성장시킬 기회를 놓치지 않을 수 있습니다."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"또한 한눈에 볼 수 있는 주요 지표들도 확인하실 수 있습니다: Added Reach, Added Streams, 그리고 플레이리스트 큐레이터에게 연락할 수 있는 직접 링크."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"아무 Track Page로 가서 Playlist 탭을 클릭하고 오늘부터 다음 플레이리스트 배치를 발견해보세요!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"pt":{"title":"Encontre sua Playlist Perfeita com Playlists to Pitch!","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Encontre a Playlist Perfeita com Playlists to Pitch!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Procurando as playlists perfeitas para divulgar sua faixa? Nossa nova funcionalidade "},{"bold":true,"text":"Playlists to Pitch "},{"text":"elimina as suposições do processo de divulgação em playlists ao recomendar playlists personalizadas especificamente para sua faixa."}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Cada recomendação vem com uma Análise de Adequação explicando exatamente por que achamos que a playlist é uma boa combinação - para que você possa divulgar com confiança e nunca perder uma oportunidade de fazer sua faixa crescer."}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Você também verá métricas importantes de relance: Alcance Adicionado, Streams Adicionados e links diretos para entrar em contato com curadores de playlists."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Acesse qualquer Página de Faixa, clique na aba Playlist e comece a descobrir seu próximo placement em playlist hoje mesmo!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/1723541b-a543-414d-916f-009ac96f00e0.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]}}'::jsonb WHERE id = 1;

UPDATE announcement_post SET translations = '{"de":{"title":"Einführung verbesserter Influencer-Einblicke im Artist UGC Tab 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Einführung verbesserter Influencer-Einblicke im Artist UGC Tab 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Die Influencer-Tabelle im Artist User Generated Contents Tab liefert jetzt reichhaltigere Daten und bessere Benutzerfreundlichkeit, um Ihnen bei der Identifizierung der richtigen Influencer für Ihre Kampagnen zu helfen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Was ist neu"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Mehr Kontext auf einen Blick: Sehen Sie Verifizierungsstatus, Top-Tracks, Hashtags und Zielgruppen-Metriken, ohne die Tabelle zu verlassen"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Intelligentere Filterung: Grenzen Sie Influencer basierend auf den Kriterien ein, die für Ihre Strategie am wichtigsten sind"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Klarere Visualisierung: Verbessertes Layout macht es einfacher, Influencer-Profile zu scannen und zu vergleichen"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Entdecken Sie die verbesserte Influencer-Tabelle in jedem Artist UGC/TikTok Tab und finden Sie Influencer, die echte Wirkung für Ihre Künstler erzielen!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"es":{"title":"Presentamos los Insights Mejorados de Influencers en la Pestaña UGC del Artista 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Presentamos Información Mejorada de Influencers en la Pestaña UGC de Artista 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"La Tabla de Influencers en la pestaña de Contenidos Generados por Usuarios del Artista ahora ofrece datos más ricos y mejor usabilidad para ayudarte a identificar los influencers correctos para tus campañas."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Qué hay de nuevo"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Más contexto de un vistazo: Ve el estado verificado, mejores canciones, hashtags y métricas de audiencia sin salir de la tabla"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Filtrado más inteligente: Reduce los influencers según los criterios que más importan para tu estrategia"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Visualización más clara: El diseño mejorado hace más fácil escanear y comparar perfiles de influencers"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"¡Explora la Tabla de Influencers actualizada en cualquier pestaña UGC/TikTok de Artista y descubre influencers que generan impacto real para tus artistas!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"fr":{"title":"Présentation des analyses d''influenceurs améliorées dans l''onglet UGC des artistes 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Présentation des Informations Améliorées sur les Influenceurs dans l''Onglet UGC Artiste 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Le Tableau des Influenceurs dans l''onglet Contenus Générés par les Utilisateurs d''Artiste offre maintenant des données plus riches et une meilleure utilisabilité pour vous aider à identifier les bons influenceurs pour vos campagnes."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Nouveautés"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Plus de contexte en un coup d''œil : Consultez le statut vérifié, les titres phares, les hashtags et les métriques d''audience sans quitter le tableau"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Filtrage plus intelligent : Affinez la sélection d''influenceurs selon les critères les plus importants pour votre stratégie"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Visualisation plus claire : La mise en page améliorée facilite la lecture et la comparaison des profils d''influenceurs"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Explorez le Tableau des Influenceurs amélioré dans n''importe quel onglet UGC/TikTok d''Artiste et découvrez les influenceurs qui génèrent un impact réel pour vos artistes !"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"ja":{"title":"Artist UGCタブでの強化されたInfluencer Insightsのご紹介 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Artist UGCタブでのInfluencer Insights強化機能のご紹介 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Artist User Generated ContentsタブのInfluencer Tableが、より豊富なデータと優れた使いやすさを提供し、キャンペーンに最適なインフルエンサーの特定をサポートします。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"新機能"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"一目でより多くの情報を確認：テーブルを離れることなく、認証ステータス、トップトラック、ハッシュタグ、オーディエンス指標を表示"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"スマートなフィルタリング：戦略に最も重要な条件に基づいてインフルエンサーを絞り込み"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"より明確な視覚化：改良されたレイアウトにより、インフルエンサープロフィールの閲覧と比較がより簡単に"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"任意のArtist UGC/TikTokタブでアップグレードされたInfluencer Tableをご活用いただき、アーティストに真のインパクトをもたらすインフルエンサーを発見してください！"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"ko":{"title":"Artist UGC 탭의 향상된 인플루언서 인사이트를 소개합니다 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Artist UGC 탭의 향상된 인플루언서 인사이트를 소개합니다 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Artist User Generated Contents 탭의 인플루언서 테이블이 이제 더 풍부한 데이터와 향상된 사용성을 제공하여 캠페인에 적합한 인플루언서를 찾을 수 있도록 도와드립니다."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"새로운 기능"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"한눈에 보는 더 많은 정보: 테이블에서 나가지 않고도 인증 상태, 인기 트랙, 해시태그, 오디언스 지표를 확인하세요"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"스마트한 필터링: 전략에 가장 중요한 기준을 바탕으로 인플루언서 범위를 좁혀보세요"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"명확한 시각화: 개선된 레이아웃으로 인플루언서 프로필을 더 쉽게 스캔하고 비교할 수 있습니다"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"모든 Artist UGC/TikTok 탭에서 업그레이드된 인플루언서 테이블을 탐색하고 아티스트에게 실질적인 영향을 미치는 인플루언서를 발견하세요!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"pt":{"title":"Apresentando Insights Aprimorados de Influenciadores na Aba UGC do Artista 🎉","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Apresentando Insights Aprimorados de Influenciadores na Aba UGC de Artistas 🎉"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"A Tabela de Influenciadores na aba User Generated Contents de Artistas agora oferece dados mais ricos e melhor usabilidade para ajudar você a identificar os influenciadores certos para suas campanhas."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Novidades"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Mais contexto de relance: Veja status verificado, faixas principais, hashtags e métricas de audiência sem sair da tabela"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Filtragem mais inteligente: Refine influenciadores com base nos critérios mais importantes para sua estratégia"}]},{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Visualização mais clara: Layout aprimorado facilita a varredura e comparação de perfis de influenciadores"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Explore a Tabela de Influenciadores atualizada em qualquer aba UGC/TikTok de Artistas e descubra influenciadores gerando impacto real para seus artistas!"}]},{"alt":"image","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/f1803c87-0b6d-4783-9eb4-bb5d10ccc5fd.png","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]}}'::jsonb WHERE id = 2;

UPDATE announcement_post SET translations = '{"de":{"title":"Einführung unserer brandneuen Navigationsleiste","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Wir stellen vor: Unsere brandneue Navigationsleiste"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Wir haben die Navigationsleiste neu gestaltet, um sie schlanker, übersichtlicher und intuitiver denn je zu machen!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Was ist neu:"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Einklappbares Design: Die Navigationsleiste erweitert sich jetzt beim Darüberfahren und gibt Ihnen mehr Bildschirmplatz, wenn Sie ihn brauchen"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Organisierte Bereiche: Elemente sind in Kategorien wie „CATALOG\" und „TOOLS\" gruppiert für schnellere Navigation"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Integrierte Suche: Finden Sie jedes Element der Navigationsleiste sofort mit der neuen Suchleiste oben"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Favoriten-Funktion: Markieren Sie Ihre meistgenutzten Elemente als Favoriten, und sie werden automatisch in einen eigenen „FAVORITES\"-Bereich für schnellen Zugriff verschoben"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Erleben Sie einen reibungsloseren, personalisierten Arbeitsablauf—probieren Sie die neue Navigationsleiste heute auf "},{"url":"https://app.chartmetric.com/artists","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Chartmetric"}]},{"text":" aus!"}]},{"alt":"chrome-capture-2025-11-24 (1)","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/6b0d7233-76c5-4ae9-bfc0-afbd82999e0b.gif","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"es":{"title":"Presentamos Nuestra Nueva Barra de Navegación","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Presentamos Nuestra Completamente Nueva Barra de Navegación"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"¡Hemos rediseñado la barra de navegación para que sea más ligera, limpia e intuitiva que nunca!"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Novedades:"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Diseño plegable: La barra de navegación ahora se expande al pasar el cursor, brindándote más espacio en pantalla cuando lo necesitas"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Secciones organizadas: Los elementos están agrupados en categorías como \"CATALOG\" y \"TOOLS\" para una navegación más rápida"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Búsqueda integrada: Encuentra cualquier elemento de la barra de navegación al instante con la nueva barra de búsqueda en la parte superior"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Función de favoritos: Marca tus elementos más utilizados como favoritos, y se moverán automáticamente a una sección dedicada \"FAVORITES\" para acceso rápido"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Experimenta un flujo de trabajo más fluido y personalizado—prueba la nueva barra de navegación hoy en "},{"url":"https://app.chartmetric.com/artists","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Chartmetric"}]},{"text":" !"}]},{"alt":"chrome-capture-2025-11-24 (1)","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/6b0d7233-76c5-4ae9-bfc0-afbd82999e0b.gif","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"fr":{"title":"Présentation de notre toute nouvelle barre de navigation","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"Présentation de notre toute nouvelle barre de navigation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Nous avons repensé la barre de navigation pour qu''elle soit plus épurée, plus claire et plus intuitive que jamais !"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"Les nouveautés :"}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Design pliable : La barre de navigation se déploie maintenant au survol, vous donnant plus d''espace d''écran quand vous en avez besoin"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Sections organisées : Les éléments sont regroupés en catégories comme \"CATALOG\" et \"TOOLS\" pour une navigation plus rapide"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Recherche intégrée : Trouvez instantanément n''importe quel élément de la barre de navigation avec la nouvelle barre de recherche en haut"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"Fonction favoris : Marquez vos éléments les plus utilisés comme favoris, et ils se déplaceront automatiquement vers une section dédiée \"FAVORITES\" pour un accès rapide"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Profitez d''un flux de travail plus fluide et plus personnalisé—découvrez la nouvelle barre de navigation dès aujourd''hui sur "},{"url":"https://app.chartmetric.com/artists","type":"link","children":[{"text":"Chartmetric"}]},{"text":" !"}]},{"alt":"chrome-capture-2025-11-24 (1)","url":"https://frill-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/2958395/6b0d7233-76c5-4ae9-bfc0-afbd82999e0b.gif","type":"image","children":[{"text":""}]}]},"ja":{"title":"新しいナビゲーションバーのご紹介","content":[{"type":"announcement-title","children":[{"text":"全く新しいナビゲーションバーのご紹介"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"ナビゲーションバーをより洗練され、クリーンで、これまで以上に直感的になるよう再設計しました！"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"bold":true,"text":"新機能："}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"折りたたみ式デザイン：ナビゲーションバーがホバー時に展開し、必要な時により多くの画面スペースを提供します"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"整理されたセクション：アイテムが「CATALOG」や「TOOLS」などのカテゴリーにグループ化され、より高速なナビゲーションが可能です"}]}]},{"type":"bulleted-list","children":[{"type":"list-item","children":[{"text":"検索機能内蔵：上部の新しい検索バーで、ナビゲーションバーの任意のアイテムを瞬時に見つけられます"